
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-medved-irs-topology-requirements-00.txt'>
    <title>"Topology API Requirements", Jan Medved, Hannes Gredler, Stefano Previdi, Shane Amante</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-medved-irs-topology-requirements-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document describes requirements for collecting topology data from network elements and other sources, creating a coherent view of the network topology from the collected data, and presenting the topology view to various applications that need to: a) understand the topology; and, b) interact/change the topology of the physical or logical network. for reflecting changes to the topology back in network elements..</description>
